{"tid":2233816,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"船隻為脫困 毀西沙海域軍用光纜","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T12:30:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"635d4ce75ea31683df4ea95d8b7bf97f9d2fd423","tid":2233816,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:00:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201007/G65IBLPPUVGWRHQZEKZB4SP4QA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201007%2FG65IBLPPUVGWRHQZEKZB4SP4QA%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmaarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=68e3b55f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201007%2FG65IBLPPUVGWRHQZEKZB4SP4QA%2F&h=a0deaefa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201007/G65IBLPPUVGWRHQZEKZB4SP4QA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n船隻為脫困 毀西沙海域軍用光纜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7lYcvDdbLhgd4hwfxNA2-W6zDaI=/1574x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MCGVJOC4IFHJNEBFL7TJLKE33I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7lYcvDdbLhgd4hwfxNA2-W6zDaI%3D%2F1574x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMCGVJOC4IFHJNEBFL7TJLKE33I.jpg&h=d925450e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉事船長被捕時供認不諱，目前取保候審。<br />\n<br />\n台海以至南海局勢波譎雲詭，海南三沙海警局早前接到報案，西沙海域的軍用海底光纜斷裂，疑遭人為破壞，因事關敏感的軍用設施，當局着手調查，發現有船隻為脫困，破壞軍用光纜，船長涉嫌觸犯「破壞軍事通信罪」，將被依法移送檢察機關起訴。<br />\n<br />\n海南三沙海警局上月初接報，西沙海域軍用海底光纜發生斷裂，三沙海警局第一時間成立專案組調查。經過比對航線、對打撈軍用海底光纜進行痕迹鑑定，確定涉案船隻。經查，有關船隻在案發海域起錨時，意外勾到疑為海底軍用光纜的鋼絲繩，為使船隻脫困，於是破壞光纜。姓王船長被捕時供認不諱，目前取保候審強制措施，並將以破壞軍事通信罪移送檢察機關起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n船長被控破壞軍事通信罪<br />\n<br />\n軍用光纜即光纖，主要用作部隊系統通訊傳輸。中國《刑法》規定，破壞武器裝備、軍事設施、軍事通信罪，可處三年以下有期徒刑、。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n環球網"},{"pid":"469163586089e828b3a634d18086da2ca46135d0","tid":2233816,"uid":269481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"阿伯好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae150afada3eae3a730c20f8b57d336f7af36957","tid":2233816,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc41b4acf46c2ea4a981d2fdea26f45821536c87","tid":2233816,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}